{
  "video_id": "vJ66jv8ICjc",
  "title": "Antony Gormley: Sculpted space, within and without",
  "es": 1,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 0.0,
      "end_time": 7000.0,
      "text": "Translator: Joseph Geni Reviewer: Morton Bast"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15920.0,
      "end_time": 20410.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m going to tell you about why I became a sculptor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 20410.0,
      "end_time": 22960.0,
      "text": "and you may think that sculptors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22960.0,
      "end_time": 27384.0,
      "text": "well, they deal with meta, they deal with objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 27385.0,
      "end_time": 30343.0,
      "text": "they deal with bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 30343.0,
      "end_time": 34886.0,
      "text": "but I think, really, what I care about most"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34886.0,
      "end_time": 38934.0,
      "text": "is making space, and that&#39;s what I&#39;ve called this talk:"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 38934.0,
      "end_time": 41541.0,
      "text": "Making Space."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 41541.0,
      "end_time": 45949.0,
      "text": "Space that exists within us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 45949.0,
      "end_time": 48180.0,
      "text": "and without us."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 48180.0,
      "end_time": 52187.0,
      "text": "So, when I was a child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 52187.0,
      "end_time": 54198.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know how many of you grew up in the &#39;50s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54198.0,
      "end_time": 59610.0,
      "text": "but I was sent upstairs for an enforced rest. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 59610.0,
      "end_time": 62957.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a really bad idea. I mean, after lunch, you&#39;re, you know,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 62957.0,
      "end_time": 66370.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re six, and you want to go and climb a tree."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 66370.0,
      "end_time": 67926.0,
      "text": "But I had to go upstairs, this tiny little room"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 67926.0,
      "end_time": 69701.0,
      "text": "that was actually made out of an old balcony,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 69701.0,
      "end_time": 74856.0,
      "text": "so it was incredibly hot, small and light,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 74856.0,
      "end_time": 78271.0,
      "text": "and I had to lie there. It was ridiculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 78271.0,
      "end_time": 80879.0,
      "text": "But anyway, for some reason, I promised myself"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 80879.0,
      "end_time": 83132.0,
      "text": "that I wasn&#39;t going to move,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 83132.0,
      "end_time": 85690.0,
      "text": "that I was going to do this thing that Mummy"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 85690.0,
      "end_time": 86996.0,
      "text": "wanted me to do."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 86996.0,
      "end_time": 90669.0,
      "text": "And there I was, lying there in this tiny space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 90669.0,
      "end_time": 97590.0,
      "text": "hot, dark, claustrophobic, matchbox-sized, behind my eyes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 97590.0,
      "end_time": 101124.0,
      "text": "but it was really weird, like, after this went on"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 101124.0,
      "end_time": 107836.0,
      "text": "for days, weeks, months, that space would get bigger"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 107837.0,
      "end_time": 111501.0,
      "text": "and darker and cooler"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 111501.0,
      "end_time": 116371.0,
      "text": "until I really looked forward to that half an hour"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 116371.0,
      "end_time": 120478.0,
      "text": "of enforced immobility and rest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 120478.0,
      "end_time": 125131.0,
      "text": "and I really looked forward to going to that place"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 125132.0,
      "end_time": 127694.0,
      "text": "of darkness."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 127694.0,
      "end_time": 130150.0,
      "text": "Do you mind if we do something completely different?"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 130150.0,
      "end_time": 132186.0,
      "text": "Can we all just close our eyes for a minute?"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 132186.0,
      "end_time": 133834.0,
      "text": "Now, this isn&#39;t going to be freaky."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 133834.0,
      "end_time": 135456.0,
      "text": "It isn&#39;t some cultic thing. (Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 135456.0,
      "end_time": 138703.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just, it&#39;s just, I just would like us all to go there."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 138704.0,
      "end_time": 140852.0,
      "text": "So I&#39;m going to do it too. We&#39;ll all be there together."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 140852.0,
      "end_time": 144687.0,
      "text": "So close your eyes for a minute."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 144687.0,
      "end_time": 147797.0,
      "text": "Here we are, in a space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 147797.0,
      "end_time": 155269.0,
      "text": "the subjective, collective space of the darkness of the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 155269.0,
      "end_time": 159324.0,
      "text": "I think of this as the place of imagination,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 159324.0,
      "end_time": 162624.0,
      "text": "of potential,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 162624.0,
      "end_time": 165524.0,
      "text": "but what are its qualities?"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 165524.0,
      "end_time": 170821.0,
      "text": "It is objectless. There are no things in it."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 170821.0,
      "end_time": 176772.0,
      "text": "It is dimensionless. It is limitless."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 176772.0,
      "end_time": 181362.0,
      "text": "It is endless."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 181362.0,
      "end_time": 183908.0,
      "text": "Okay, open your eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 183908.0,
      "end_time": 188117.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s the space that I think sculpture --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 188117.0,
      "end_time": 191185.0,
      "text": "which is a bit of a paradox, sculpture that is about"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 191185.0,
      "end_time": 194529.0,
      "text": "making material propositions --"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 194529.0,
      "end_time": 196650.0,
      "text": "but I think that&#39;s the space"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 196650.0,
      "end_time": 201318.0,
      "text": "that sculpture can connect us with."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 201318.0,
      "end_time": 205503.0,
      "text": "So, imagine we&#39;re in the middle of America."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 205503.0,
      "end_time": 208375.0,
      "text": "You&#39;re asleep. You wake up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 208375.0,
      "end_time": 211722.0,
      "text": "and without lifting your head from the earth"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 211722.0,
      "end_time": 217160.0,
      "text": "on your sleeping bag, you can see for 70 miles."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 217160.0,
      "end_time": 220411.0,
      "text": "This is a dry lake bed."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 220411.0,
      "end_time": 224653.0,
      "text": "I was young. I&#39;d just finished art school."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 224653.0,
      "end_time": 226825.0,
      "text": "I wanted to do something that was working"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 226825.0,
      "end_time": 231976.0,
      "text": "directly with the world, directly with place."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 231977.0,
      "end_time": 235400.0,
      "text": "This was a wonderful place, because it was a place"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 235400.0,
      "end_time": 237257.0,
      "text": "where you could imagine that you were the"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 237257.0,
      "end_time": 239591.0,
      "text": "first person to be there."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 239591.0,
      "end_time": 244500.0,
      "text": "It was a place where nothing very much had happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 244500.0,
      "end_time": 247745.0,
      "text": "Anyway, bear with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 247745.0,
      "end_time": 251530.0,
      "text": "I picked up a hand-sized stone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 251530.0,
      "end_time": 253623.0,
      "text": "threw it as far as I was able,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 253623.0,
      "end_time": 255694.0,
      "text": "it was about 22 meters."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 255694.0,
      "end_time": 262310.0,
      "text": "I then cleared all the stones within that radius"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 262310.0,
      "end_time": 265834.0,
      "text": "and made a pile."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 265834.0,
      "end_time": 268238.0,
      "text": "And that was the pile, by the way."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 268238.0,
      "end_time": 271735.0,
      "text": "And then, I stood on the pile,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 271735.0,
      "end_time": 275604.0,
      "text": "and threw all of those rocks out again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 275604.0,
      "end_time": 280822.0,
      "text": "and here is rearranged desert."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 280822.0,
      "end_time": 282800.0,
      "text": "You could say, well, it doesn&#39;t look very different"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 282800.0,
      "end_time": 284919.0,
      "text": "from when he started."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 284919.0,
      "end_time": 286121.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 286122.0,
      "end_time": 287756.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s all the fuss about?"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 287756.0,
      "end_time": 289123.0,
      "text": "In fact, Chris was worried and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 289124.0,
      "end_time": 290518.0,
      "text": "\"Look, don&#39;t show them that slide,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 290518.0,
      "end_time": 292477.0,
      "text": "because they&#39;re just going to think you&#39;re another one of"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 292477.0,
      "end_time": 295143.0,
      "text": "those crazy modern artists who doesn&#39;t do much."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 295143.0,
      "end_time": 297513.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 297513.0,
      "end_time": 304222.0,
      "text": "But the fact is, this is evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 304222.0,
      "end_time": 307757.0,
      "text": "of a living body on other bodies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 307757.0,
      "end_time": 313596.0,
      "text": "rocks that have been the subject of geological formation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 313596.0,
      "end_time": 318610.0,
      "text": "erosion, the action of time on objects."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 318610.0,
      "end_time": 321132.0,
      "text": "This is a place, in a way, that I just"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 321132.0,
      "end_time": 324613.0,
      "text": "would like you to, in a way, look at differently"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 324613.0,
      "end_time": 328284.0,
      "text": "because of this event that has happened in it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 328284.0,
      "end_time": 330339.0,
      "text": "a human event,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 330339.0,
      "end_time": 333891.0,
      "text": "and in general, it just asks us to look again"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 333891.0,
      "end_time": 336450.0,
      "text": "at this world, so different from, in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 336450.0,
      "end_time": 339721.0,
      "text": "the world that we have been sharing with each other,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 339721.0,
      "end_time": 342147.0,
      "text": "the technological world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 342147.0,
      "end_time": 346841.0,
      "text": "to look again at the elemental world."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 346841.0,
      "end_time": 352550.0,
      "text": "The elemental world that we all live in is that space"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 352550.0,
      "end_time": 356938.0,
      "text": "that we all visited together, the darkness of the body."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 356938.0,
      "end_time": 360603.0,
      "text": "I wanted to start again with that environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 360603.0,
      "end_time": 364273.0,
      "text": "the environment of the intimate, subjective space"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 364273.0,
      "end_time": 368990.0,
      "text": "that each of us lives in, but from the other side"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 368990.0,
      "end_time": 370707.0,
      "text": "of appearance."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 370707.0,
      "end_time": 373131.0,
      "text": "So here is a daily activity of the studio."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 373131.0,
      "end_time": 376770.0,
      "text": "You can see I don&#39;t do much. I&#39;m just standing there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 376770.0,
      "end_time": 379496.0,
      "text": "again with my eyes closed, and other people"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 379497.0,
      "end_time": 384240.0,
      "text": "are molding me, evidential."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 384240.0,
      "end_time": 387672.0,
      "text": "This is an indexical register of a lived moment"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 387672.0,
      "end_time": 390855.0,
      "text": "of a body in time."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 390855.0,
      "end_time": 396578.0,
      "text": "Can we map that space, using the language of neutrinos"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 396578.0,
      "end_time": 401364.0,
      "text": "or cosmic rays, taking the bounding condition of the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 401364.0,
      "end_time": 406839.0,
      "text": "as its limit, but in complete reversal of, in a way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 406839.0,
      "end_time": 409462.0,
      "text": "the most traditional Greek idea of pointing?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 409462.0,
      "end_time": 413250.0,
      "text": "In the old days they used to take a lump of Pentelic marble"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 413250.0,
      "end_time": 417908.0,
      "text": "and drill from the surface in order to identify the skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 417908.0,
      "end_time": 419360.0,
      "text": "the appearance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 419360.0,
      "end_time": 422621.0,
      "text": "what Aristotle defined as the distinction"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 422621.0,
      "end_time": 424644.0,
      "text": "between substance and appearance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 424644.0,
      "end_time": 427711.0,
      "text": "the thing that makes things visible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 427711.0,
      "end_time": 430766.0,
      "text": "but here we&#39;re working from the other side."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 430766.0,
      "end_time": 434811.0,
      "text": "Or can we do it as an exclusive membrane?"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 434811.0,
      "end_time": 440769.0,
      "text": "This is a lead case made around the space"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 440769.0,
      "end_time": 444234.0,
      "text": "that my body occupied, but it&#39;s now void."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 444234.0,
      "end_time": 448108.0,
      "text": "This is a work called \"Learning To See.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 448108.0,
      "end_time": 454392.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a bit of, well, we could call it night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 454392.0,
      "end_time": 458842.0,
      "text": "we could call it the 96 percent of gravity"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 458842.0,
      "end_time": 462402.0,
      "text": "that we don&#39;t know about, dark matter,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 462403.0,
      "end_time": 465948.0,
      "text": "placed in space, anyway, another version of a human space"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 465948.0,
      "end_time": 468861.0,
      "text": "in space at large, but I don&#39;t know if you can see,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 468861.0,
      "end_time": 474930.0,
      "text": "the eyes are indicated, they&#39;re closed."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 474930.0,
      "end_time": 478393.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s called \"Learning To See\" because it&#39;s about an object"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 478393.0,
      "end_time": 482724.0,
      "text": "that hopefully works reflexively and talks about that"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 482725.0,
      "end_time": 486544.0,
      "text": "vision or connection with the darkness of the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 486544.0,
      "end_time": 491517.0,
      "text": "that I see as a space of potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 491517.0,
      "end_time": 494592.0,
      "text": "Can we do it another way, using the language"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 494592.0,
      "end_time": 497777.0,
      "text": "of particles around a nucleus, and talk about the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 497778.0,
      "end_time": 499708.0,
      "text": "as an energy center?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 499708.0,
      "end_time": 502766.0,
      "text": "No longer about statues, no longer having to take that"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 502766.0,
      "end_time": 505827.0,
      "text": "duty of standing, the standing of a human body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 505827.0,
      "end_time": 509157.0,
      "text": "or the standing of a statue, release it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 509157.0,
      "end_time": 513414.0,
      "text": "allow it to be an energy field, a space in space"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 513414.0,
      "end_time": 520236.0,
      "text": "that talks about human life, between becoming an entropy"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 520236.0,
      "end_time": 524980.0,
      "text": "as a sort of concentration of attention,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 524980.0,
      "end_time": 530490.0,
      "text": "a human place of possibility in space at large."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 530490.0,
      "end_time": 533824.0,
      "text": "Is there another way?"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 533825.0,
      "end_time": 539924.0,
      "text": "Dark matter now placed against a horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 539924.0,
      "end_time": 543959.0,
      "text": "If minds live in bodies, if bodies live in clothes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 543959.0,
      "end_time": 547890.0,
      "text": "and then in rooms, and then in buildings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 547890.0,
      "end_time": 552791.0,
      "text": "and then in cities, do they also have a final skin,"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 552791.0,
      "end_time": 555424.0,
      "text": "and is that skin perceptual?"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 555424.0,
      "end_time": 558450.0,
      "text": "The horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 558460.0,
      "end_time": 560547.0,
      "text": "And is art about"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 560547.0,
      "end_time": 566475.0,
      "text": "trying to imagine what lies beyond the horizon?"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 566491.0,
      "end_time": 575112.0,
      "text": "Can we use, in a way, a body as an empty catalyst"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 575112.0,
      "end_time": 579863.0,
      "text": "for a kind of empathy with the experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 579863.0,
      "end_time": 585211.0,
      "text": "of space-time as it is lived, as I am standing here"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 585211.0,
      "end_time": 590605.0,
      "text": "in front of you trying to feel and make a connection"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 590605.0,
      "end_time": 593911.0,
      "text": "in this space-time that we are sharing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 593911.0,
      "end_time": 597467.0,
      "text": "can we use, at it were, the memory of a body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 597467.0,
      "end_time": 600290.0,
      "text": "of a human space in space to catalyze"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 600291.0,
      "end_time": 604140.0,
      "text": "an experience, again, firsthand experience,"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 604140.0,
      "end_time": 607210.0,
      "text": "of elemental time."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 607210.0,
      "end_time": 611545.0,
      "text": "Human time, industrial time, tested against"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 611545.0,
      "end_time": 614540.0,
      "text": "the time of the tides, in which these memories"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 614541.0,
      "end_time": 619500.0,
      "text": "of a particular body, that could be any body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 619500.0,
      "end_time": 624390.0,
      "text": "multiplied as in the time of mechanical reproduction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 624390.0,
      "end_time": 628775.0,
      "text": "many times, placed over three square miles,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 628775.0,
      "end_time": 632429.0,
      "text": "a mile out to sea,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 632429.0,
      "end_time": 636784.0,
      "text": "disappearing, in different conditions of day and night."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 636784.0,
      "end_time": 640530.0,
      "text": "You can see this work. It&#39;s on the mouth of the Mersey,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 640530.0,
      "end_time": 643210.0,
      "text": "just outside Liverpool."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 643210.0,
      "end_time": 646675.0,
      "text": "And there you can see what a Liverpool sea looks like"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 646675.0,
      "end_time": 649501.0,
      "text": "on a typical afternoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 649501.0,
      "end_time": 652203.0,
      "text": "The pieces appear and disappear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 652203.0,
      "end_time": 654266.0,
      "text": "but maybe more importantly --"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 654266.0,
      "end_time": 658199.0,
      "text": "this is just looking north from the center of the installation --"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 658199.0,
      "end_time": 662536.0,
      "text": "they create a field, a field that involves"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 662536.0,
      "end_time": 668297.0,
      "text": "living and the surrogate bodies in a kind of relation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 668298.0,
      "end_time": 673259.0,
      "text": "a relation with each other and a relation with that limit,"
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 673259.0,
      "end_time": 677500.0,
      "text": "the edge, the horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 677500.0,
      "end_time": 679507.0,
      "text": "Just moving on, is it possible,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 679507.0,
      "end_time": 684189.0,
      "text": "taking that idea of mind, body, body-building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 684190.0,
      "end_time": 687595.0,
      "text": "to supplant the first body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 687595.0,
      "end_time": 689575.0,
      "text": "the biological body, with the second,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 689575.0,
      "end_time": 692493.0,
      "text": "the body of architecture and the built environment."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 692493.0,
      "end_time": 697840.0,
      "text": "This is a work called \"Room for the Great Australian Desert.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 697840.0,
      "end_time": 698702.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s in an undefined location"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 698702.0,
      "end_time": 701783.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;ve never published where it is."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 701783.0,
      "end_time": 703673.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s an object for the mind."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 703673.0,
      "end_time": 707940.0,
      "text": "I think of it as a 21st-century Buddha."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 707940.0,
      "end_time": 709240.0,
      "text": "Again, the darkness of the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 709240.0,
      "end_time": 712870.0,
      "text": "now held within this bunker shape"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 712870.0,
      "end_time": 715571.0,
      "text": "of the minimum position that a body needs to occupy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 715571.0,
      "end_time": 717687.0,
      "text": "a crouching body."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 717687.0,
      "end_time": 720674.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a hole at the anus, penis level."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 720674.0,
      "end_time": 723411.0,
      "text": "There are holes at ears. There are no holes at the eyes."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 723411.0,
      "end_time": 727665.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s a slot for the mouth. It&#39;s two and a half inches thick,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 727665.0,
      "end_time": 730400.0,
      "text": "concrete with a void interior."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 730400.0,
      "end_time": 734187.0,
      "text": "Again, a site found with a completely flat"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 734187.0,
      "end_time": 738883.0,
      "text": "360-degree horizon."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 738883.0,
      "end_time": 743207.0,
      "text": "This is just simply asking, again,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 743207.0,
      "end_time": 747795.0,
      "text": "as if we had arrived for the first time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 747795.0,
      "end_time": 751930.0,
      "text": "what is the relationship of the human project"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 751931.0,
      "end_time": 756440.0,
      "text": "to time and space?"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 756440.0,
      "end_time": 759617.0,
      "text": "Taking that idiom of, as it were,"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 759617.0,
      "end_time": 764610.0,
      "text": "the darkness of the body transferred to architecture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 764610.0,
      "end_time": 768185.0,
      "text": "can you use architectural space not for living"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 768185.0,
      "end_time": 769897.0,
      "text": "but as a metaphor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 769898.0,
      "end_time": 773675.0,
      "text": "and use its systolic, diastolic"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 773675.0,
      "end_time": 778493.0,
      "text": "smaller and larger spaces to provide a kind of"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 778494.0,
      "end_time": 784166.0,
      "text": "firsthand somatic narrative for a journey through space,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 784166.0,
      "end_time": 787462.0,
      "text": "light and darkness?"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 787462.0,
      "end_time": 792984.0,
      "text": "This is a work of some proportion and some weight"
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 792984.0,
      "end_time": 797870.0,
      "text": "that makes the body into a city, an aggregation of cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 797870.0,
      "end_time": 800282.0,
      "text": "that are all interconnected"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 800282.0,
      "end_time": 805114.0,
      "text": "and that allow certain visual access"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 805114.0,
      "end_time": 807913.0,
      "text": "at certain places."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 807913.0,
      "end_time": 814616.0,
      "text": "The last work that I just wanted to share with you"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 814616.0,
      "end_time": 818418.0,
      "text": "is \"Blind Light,\" which is perhaps"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 818418.0,
      "end_time": 821678.0,
      "text": "the most open work,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 821678.0,
      "end_time": 823813.0,
      "text": "and in a conference of radical openness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 823813.0,
      "end_time": 827821.0,
      "text": "I think maybe this is as radical as I get,"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 827821.0,
      "end_time": 832840.0,
      "text": "using light and water vapor as my materials."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 832840.0,
      "end_time": 834469.0,
      "text": "Here is a box"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 834470.0,
      "end_time": 838120.0,
      "text": "filled at one and a half atmospheres of atmospheric pressure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 838120.0,
      "end_time": 842500.0,
      "text": "with a cloud and with very bright light."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 842510.0,
      "end_time": 845472.0,
      "text": "As you walk towards the ever-open threshold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 845472.0,
      "end_time": 853384.0,
      "text": "you disappear, both to yourselves and to others."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 853384.0,
      "end_time": 855540.0,
      "text": "If you hold your hand out in front of you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 855540.0,
      "end_time": 857394.0,
      "text": "you can&#39;t see it."
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 857394.0,
      "end_time": 860660.0,
      "text": "If you look down, you can&#39;t see your feet."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 860660.0,
      "end_time": 867661.0,
      "text": "You are now consciousness without an object,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 867662.0,
      "end_time": 871555.0,
      "text": "freed from the dimensionful"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 871555.0,
      "end_time": 877440.0,
      "text": "and measured way in which life links us"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 877441.0,
      "end_time": 880531.0,
      "text": "to the obligatory."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 880531.0,
      "end_time": 885507.0,
      "text": "But this is a space that is actually filled with people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 885508.0,
      "end_time": 887478.0,
      "text": "disembodied voices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 887478.0,
      "end_time": 891592.0,
      "text": "and out of that ambient environment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 891592.0,
      "end_time": 895521.0,
      "text": "when people come close to your own body zone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 895522.0,
      "end_time": 899585.0,
      "text": "very close, they appear to you as representations."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 899585.0,
      "end_time": 901805.0,
      "text": "When they appear close to the edge,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 901805.0,
      "end_time": 906388.0,
      "text": "they are representations, representations in which"
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 906389.0,
      "end_time": 910257.0,
      "text": "the viewers have become the viewed."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 910257.0,
      "end_time": 916108.0,
      "text": "For me, art is not about objects of high monetary exchange."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 916108.0,
      "end_time": 921512.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s about reasserting our firsthand experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 921513.0,
      "end_time": 924404.0,
      "text": "in present time."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 924404.0,
      "end_time": 927845.0,
      "text": "As John Cage said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 927845.0,
      "end_time": 932932.0,
      "text": "\"We are not moving towards some kind of goal."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 932932.0,
      "end_time": 937613.0,
      "text": "We are at the goal, and it is changing with us."
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 937613.0,
      "end_time": 944490.0,
      "text": "If art has any purpose, it is to open our eyes to that fact.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 944490.0,
      "end_time": 946860.0,
      "text": "Thank you very much."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 946860.0,
      "end_time": 950253.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}